channel.title: I log into my account and it loggs me back out .. help
channel.description:
hey i was just on my account a minute ago and it froze like normal. so i closed moparscape and tried it again, i get logged in, it shows all the updates at the bottom, and then just sits on the loading screen ... and on the DOS at the bottom it says i looged in, character saved, then the clienthandler disconnects me ..
any advice please?[br][size=1]Posted at: July 28, 2006, 10:53:33 PM[/size][hr]i was trying to spawn something and it froze up[br][size=1]Posted at: July 28, 2006, 11:34:19 PM[/size][hr]anyone please?

Another way if something happens like that is stay on the same server and make another acocunt and when in that account type ::saveme but dont press enter. Then log in to your other account and quickly press enter and it will bring you somewhere and you shouldn’t have the problem anymore.
